==English==
===Etymology===
:'''[[drive]]''' + '''[[-er]]'''

===Noun===
'''driver'''

# a person who drives a motorized vehicle, such as a car or a bus
# a person who drives some other vehicle
# In computer terminology, a '''driver''' is a special [[program]] that acts as an [[interface]] between the [[application]] program and the [[computer]] [[hardware]]. Drivers are written specifically for the hardware device they control. 

